Dr Christian Engels

I am a University Lecturer (Assistant Professor) in the UK with research interests in Banking, Household Finance and Behavioural Finance. My work has appeared in the European Journal of Finance and the Journal of Banking and Finance. I enjoy using data science tools such as R, Git, Docker and VS Code.
